item.title: Worldcraft Online
item.description: Welcome to Minecraft 4D mini games. Here you will find exciting adventures on a desert island full of bloodthirsty zombies and dangerous traps. At the beginning of the game, you are given time to prepare for the attack of the risen dead. Do not waste time and build defensive redoubts for yourself from the available building materials. The game will delight you with original and thoughtful graphics, as well as excellent sound effects.
